<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_fa7bc00c-16f0-4297-a30c-90930fda4733" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>7.3.2</sptc><title id="_7fb229da-66fe-4f9c-bb7a-9b4024b4b060">Fixing of roof tiles and ancillaries</title><archive-num>2019: 3.5.2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_ad11b8ae-eb93-4ac9-abd2-34a5cc7681c4" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ff52563e-022c-4944-a6ed-e44e700b3394">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Roof tiles and hip, ridge, barge and capping tiles must be fixed in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/388_1.2.0.xml#_942d2b2c-0899-4bf0-a6c1-22f059333c7e" id="_fa81610f-ad51-4a09-8b04-7741770055f9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table 7.3.2</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/652_0.7.0.xml#_be766c9b-9ae9-4c81-8605-95c520977b8e" id="_30363ce4-5d5e-468f-8cab-b0dd212c71d0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2a</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/653_0.11.0.xml#_fdfa520c-9cf6-4382-b6f9-c3107d9a4833" id="_abde7d89-d0b7-4710-9538-cb8aba7daac6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2b</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/654_0.6.0.xml#_4ce05757-90e4-4dc3-a604-7712f2253c61" id="_050b1829-cb31-4dc3-868f-b871c0daf43d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2c</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/656_0.6.0.xml#_ae7e5a1d-111f-46d5-ad88-b8e1f2dc1f2f" id="_b729146b-d35b-4646-861b-2cc4eae6caa6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2d</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/657_0.9.0.xml#_6e93b310-ffd7-4b97-8ade-88acb2949ebe" id="_3031d4de-5557-40ad-8682-32794eb1ca1c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2e</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_5e28eda1-d503-4228-8093-2b87c9fc1e6e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f012ba05-fdce-4ff9-a4c6-af5a4c501b03">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Fixing <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_2ef4af7d-d30f-42c6-a1df-68713386112d" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/388_1.2.0.xml#_942d2b2c-0899-4bf0-a6c1-22f059333c7e" id="_3ee03b46-26b3-457d-b6a7-f71d9d0c25c1" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table 7.3.2</xref> must consist of one or a combination of the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_04da46ac-311e-411e-b6cd-525f6977d88f">Galvanized clout nails with a minimum diameter of 2.8 mm and of a length so that the nail will penetrate not less than 15 mm into the batten.</li><li id="_c7bba480-b6ea-4f92-9f30-40f50b5583de">Self embedding head screws of 8-18 gauge and of a length so that the screw will penetrate not less than 15 mm into the batten.</li><li id="_191d6729-de64-4ce4-9a61-b658d9846b36">Purpose made clips of non-ferrous metal, stainless steel or steel protected from corrosion in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/378_0.4.0.xml#_24ccf8f5-33a9-40f6-8a50-e7c7fa190501" id="_7aa4a79f-67e4-4ab9-adec-1098256599ba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Tables 7.2.2b</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/379_0.4.0.xml#_48c5c9cf-2aa9-4ee1-a596-6c55a6a23a9a" id="_900f1873-cdf2-4cf5-9fc6-ed14332da26b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">7.2.2c</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/380_0.5.0.xml#_73e99833-ec9a-4a3c-8047-433f32044cb7" id="_70f7ec2b-985e-47e1-9953-53481cfb6985" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">7.2.2d</xref>.</li><li id="_3edd6eb8-15cc-4dcb-b086-1fc4152e0045">Flexible pointing material complying with AS 2050.</li></ol></subclause><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/388_1.2.0.xml" graph="None" id="_942d2b2c-0899-4bf0-a6c1-22f059333c7e"><num>7.3.2</num><title id="_500e7b2b-3e93-4254-9cd2-bf2f9b7517ea">Minimum fixing requirements</title><table id="_19013784-8a4c-4cc7-b502-790c7c408df3" keycol="1"><tgroup cols="4"><colspec colname="001" colnum="1" colwidth="108.00*"/><colspec colname="002" colnum="2" colwidth="108.00*"/><colspec colname="003" colnum="3" colwidth="108.00*"/><colspec colname="004" colnum="4" colwidth="108.00*"/><thead><row><entry>Wind class</entry><entry>Tile fixing - edge of roof</entry><entry>Tile fixing - field of roof</entry><entry>Ridge, hip, barge and valley tiles including capping (see <xref format="dita" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2d-fixing-of-ridge-capping-ridge-clip-fixing.xml#_ae7e5a1d-111f-46d5-ad88-b8e1f2dc1f2f" id="_32e519d6-d8a3-422d-b07b-d9f6f4d964bd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2d</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2e-fixing-of-hip-capping-clout-or-screw-fixing.xml#_6e93b310-ffd7-4b97-8ade-88acb2949ebe" id="_cf382caf-2863-471b-a6c4-75e461adb8f3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">7.3.2e</xref>)</entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry>N1 and N2</entry><entry>Fix every full tile in second course in from the edge of roof.</entry><entry>In field of roof fix every second tile in every course, or every tile in each alternative course. (see <xref format="dita" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2b-fixing-of-tile-requirements-minimum-tile-fixing-requirements-N1-N2.xml#_fdfa520c-9cf6-4382-b6f9-c3107d9a4833" id="_d8c3fb11-aee9-4c14-9a8e-bb95212779d8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2b</xref>)</entry><entry>Fix each tile</entry></row><row><entry>N3</entry><entry>Fix each full tile in every second course starting from the second course in (see <xref format="dita" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2c-fixing-of-tile-requirements-minimum-tile-fixing-requirements-N3.xml#_4ce05757-90e4-4dc3-a604-7712f2253c61" id="_58b08404-1f32-4415-8bd3-ffc75bcf00df" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2c</xref>)</entry><entry>Fix every second full tile in every course (see <xref format="dita" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2c-fixing-of-tile-requirements-minimum-tile-fixing-requirements-N3.xml#_4ce05757-90e4-4dc3-a604-7712f2253c61" id="_cc09fd3a-22db-497a-a8ec-f0d3ede4d7b6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2c</xref>)</entry><entry>Fix each tile</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><desc-note id="_adfd37d4-4931-4ddc-a03d-315358f64a64"><p>Refer to <xref format="dita" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2a-fixing-of-tile-requirements-identification-of-field-and-edge-of-roof.xml#_be766c9b-9ae9-4c81-8605-95c520977b8e" id="_cbba08f9-4420-430b-b01f-bbedb557a8f5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.2a</xref> for determination of ‘edge of roof’ and ‘field of roof’.</p></desc-note></table-reference><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/652_0.7.0.xml" id="_be766c9b-9ae9-4c81-8605-95c520977b8e"><num>7.3.2a</num><title id="_4e3794c5-304b-4202-a072-749d3fcced24">Fixing of tile requirements — Identification of field and edge of roof</title><image alt="Fixing of tile requirements — Identification of field and edge of roof" height="578" heightdpi="200" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2a-fixing-of-tile-requirements-identification-of-field-and-edge-of-roof.eps" width="1105" widthdpi="200"><image height="578" heightdpi="200" href="C:\Users\bkiem\AppData\Roaming\Quark\XML Author\Temp\media1_c7ad51b5-60a3-456e-bb66-3fba9b338b1a.jpg" width="1105" widthdpi="200"/></image></image-reference><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/653_0.11.0.xml" id="_fdfa520c-9cf6-4382-b6f9-c3107d9a4833"><num xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" inv:access="external">7.3.2b</num><title xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_17e837a6-ef93-40fd-8d5a-57003c2c4870" inv:access="external">Fixing of tile requirements — Minimum tile fixing requirements - Wind class N1/N2</title><image xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:7-3-2b-fixing-of-tile-requirements-minimum-tile-fixing-requirements-N1-N2.eps" inv:access="external"/></image-reference><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/654_0.6.0.xml" id="_4ce05757-90e4-4dc3-a604-7712f2253c61"><num xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" inv:access="external">7.3.2c</num><title xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_ff3f9b3b-8658-49e0-a157-647086ca0542" i